=====================
= OpenMEEG software =
=====================

The OpenMEEG software is a C++ package for solving the forward
problem of electroencephalography and magnetoencephalography.

This software is governed by the CeCILL-B license under French law (See LICENSE file).

Contact : openmeeg-info@lists.gforge.inria.fr

Copyright INRIA and ENPC (contributors: Geoffray ADDE, Maureen CLERC, Alexandre
GRAMFORT, Renaud KERIVEN, Jan KYBIC, Perrine LANDREAU, Theodore PAPADOPOULO,
Maureen.Clerc.AT.sophia.inria.fr, keriven.AT.certis.enpc.fr,
kybic.AT.fel.cvut.cz, papadop.AT.sophia.inria.fr, Alexandre.Gramfort.AT.inria.fr)

